{"tid":1676372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動PO] 建議每個星期六例牌行動為「光復連儂牆」","createTime":"2019-10-26T11:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T05:24:07.000Z","uid":108757,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"a900db37509cdbccf11b07f1bd60c7e45ab440d6","tid":1676372,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:51:46.000Z","msg":"連儂牆嘅精神就係撕一貼百，宜家得返「撕一」，「貼百」唔見咗，就連食環都嚟剷牆。連儂牆係文宣嘅重要據點，不能失守。宜家相對活動少咗，好應該做返好文宣，而唔係休息！而「光復連儂牆」行動就係逢星期六，每人帶一啲自己最中意嘅文宣，去平時去開嘅連儂牆，幫連儂牆翻新嘅行動。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">目的及好處︰</span><br />\n1. 堅持初心，撕一貼百<br />\n2. 多人，唔使怕貼野俾人打<br />\n3. 抗爭恆常化，融入生活<br />\n4. 可以清舊文宣，貼新文宣，維持新鮮感<br />\n5. 盡量幫手分返文宣類別，令連儂牆變成藝術品<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家可以參考</span><br />\n[文宣入]元朗國連儂牆又勁左<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1669508\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1669508</a><br />\n<br />\n葵芳連儂牆又有靚野！！！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1673868\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1673868</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣建議方向︰</span><br />\n1. 行動文宣 (最當眼位置)<br />\n宣傳下星期大大小小嘅活動，令街坊知道日期同時間。<br />\n<br />\n2. 解釋大眾對抗爭之誤解<br />\n幫手解釋點解要裝修、點解以武制暴、點解爆黨鐵......令大眾明白抗爭者行動背後理念，從而得到大眾諒解及支持。<br />\n<br />\n3. 藝術作品、打卡位<br />\n連豬、PEPE、勇武畫作、特大幅作品......作用係吸引眼球，鼓勵市民影相PO上IG，同埋停低慢慢睇<br />\n<br />\n4. 心聲MEMO紙<br />\n俾人寫低最抗爭嘅睇法，係連儂牆最開始嘅形態<br />\n<br />\n5. 區議會選舉資訊<br />\n張貼區內候選人嘅「風光事跡」，配以大頭相，加以表揚，等街坊認住佢個樣，同佢做過咩好事<br />\n<br />\n6. 自行發揮<br />\n<br />\n最緊要係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「人多」、「分類」、「定時」、「創意」</span>，將連儂牆變成藝術品，手足們快啲印文宣喇！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"4647f93a0d7c0a8e808185b211319b0bd412e030","tid":1676372,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:52:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f95239f20896db15108cd307b5f4885f1467a1c0","tid":1676372,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:54:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"befdb8ce1ffe7b93c64fca767eecf775bc488cba","tid":1676372,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:56:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cd7ceaac4e64feb8413ba8884813723de54f317","tid":1676372,"uid":174476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:58:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e63af36295bab031541ebcdcbaf87e8abe4072a1","tid":1676372,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:58:48.000Z","msg":"行動PO魔咒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa8e09b22a5040ee17d0bfd5c4acb8c4ffe22fa","tid":1676372,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:59:03.000Z","msg":"連儂牆呢個好有威力，佢哋其實好驚呢樣嘢"},{"pid":"30f28a5461f9bb6b81ad554d55285327e9d28098","tid":1676372,"uid":18960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:00:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c350d69b56565a1cf7ded64753557c88399e262c","tid":1676372,"uid":269372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:00:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7826bb90e4eed6a42847f997faff0602e29484c","tid":1676372,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:01:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"addd73b55318367905478069fac6481c6919e737","tid":1676372,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:02:03.000Z","msg":"而家對貼文宣都冷淡左好多<br />\n場運動都去到尾聲啦"},{"pid":"21